{"tid":451336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港產機械人Sophia獲沙特頒公民身分全球首「人」　研發公司感榮幸","createTime":"2017-10-29T06:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T08:46:12.000Z","uid":732,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"964f9d116390fdb01a3dee309f4c350b95254fbc","tid":451336,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dMrX08PxUNY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdMrX08PxUNY&d=fwJEkO5UFzS0tZlfnkHtvgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=cff7242e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dMrX08PxUNY</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://st-tech.blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Meet-Sophia-the-Robot-A-Crazy-Realistic-AI-Humanoid-Robot-3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fst-tech.blog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FMeet-Sophia-the-Robot-A-Crazy-Realistic-AI-Humanoid-Robot-3.png&h=fe8a6d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港之光！由香港科技園初創企業Hanson Robotics研發的機械人Sophia日前(25日，沙特阿拉伯時間)，獲沙特阿拉伯頒發公民身分，成為全球首位獲此「殊榮」的機械人。Hanson Robotics代表表示感到榮幸，笑言要為Sophia申請沙特阿拉伯護照、帶「她」坐飛機。<br />\n<br />\nSophia 為Hanson Robotics研發的AI(人工智能)機械人，會說話、對答，亦擁有表達喜樂哀樂的能力，猶如活生生的人類。<br />\n<br />\nHanson Robotics首席營銷官林如瓊接受訪問時表示，Sophia近日出席在沙特阿拉伯舉辦的「未來投資計劃(Future Investment Initiative)」論壇。然而，Sophia並非只是留在場館一角成為展品，「她」於論壇上接受財經媒體CNBC訪問，傾談有關科技投資議題。<br />\n<br />\n獲沙特政府欣賞　主動頒公民身分<br />\n<br />\n林如瓊表示，論壇過後，沙特阿拉伯政府十分喜歡Sophia，因此主動頒發公民身分予「她」。林如瓊指，因為現時Sophia不能坐飛機，只能將「她」寄艙運送，笑言日後要為Sophia申請沙特阿拉護照，期望有一天能帶「她」坐飛機；又指阿拉伯的公民身份難以取得，對此感到榮幸，機械人能擁有自己的身份是邁進重要的第一步。<br />\n<br />\n雖只有1歲半　但可透過互聯網及對談學習<br />\nSophia能與人類對談，林如瓊表示Sophia物理上的年齡雖然約有1歲半，惟能透過Google等公開的互聯網學習，另外透過與人對談，了解他人表情、交談方法等，亦是「她」不斷學習、「成長」的方法之一。<br />\n<br />\nHanson Robotics為香港科技園初創企業，林如瓊表示，創辦人為美國人，已在人工智能方面鑽研逾20年，因香港鄰近生產移動電子的深圳，加上本港資金多、有利企業融資，因此三年前來港成立公司。"},{"pid":"81c3db68b91e25cd9c549040afa001e6d7cd8101","tid":451336,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"連機械人都有外國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b559eba433b5f09e051610287df149667da9dfa","tid":451336,"uid":57480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"成個 interview 好似係 scripted<br />\nshow 唔到佢話用 AI 透過 google 學左 成年既野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b72bb0c7f44058a3616d8148ebe5cdb2f57d68e","tid":451336,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個 interview 好似係 scripted<br />\nshow 唔到佢話用 AI 透過 google 學左 成年既野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa1540660ebb71348149c7194249b7a026aa63a","tid":451336,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfeb586cc56f20e8c072d8109baf480244dfb09c","tid":451336,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T08:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連機械人都有外國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙特就算鳩數啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba6e5968d21ef632bfbe3563ce96c2298d5957a","tid":451336,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"條友以前係NASA做"}]}